description: "Map of Saleijer (Selayar)—an island off the south coast of Celebes (Sulawesi)—and nearby islands. Settlements and roads are shown, including a long road along the west coast which links cities marked with a Dutch flag, illustrating colonial rule."
title: "Kaart van de afdeeling, eiland Saleijer (Silaijara) COLLBN Port 62 N 29"
